description:
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for an experienced Band 6 Dietitianto join the Staff Bank, based at the Queen Alexandra Hospital, Portsmouth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a line of work available starting for 37.5 hours a week, Monday to Friday 9-5. We require the role filled ASAP to cover a vacancy in our Macmillan badged post working with oncology outpatients&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Portsmouth is one of the largest NHS trusts in the country. Joining the Staff Bank we can offer you a more flexible shift pattern, as well as the opportunities to work across different departments, gaining invaluable skills and experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential Requirements;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree/Diploma in Dietetics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HCPC Registered Dietitian&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 - 2 years postgraduate experience including experience of acute hospital and/or home enteral feeding (HETF) dietetics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evidence of professional development or commitment to postgraduate study&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Right to work in the UK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communications skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Bank members are invaluable to us and in return for their dedication and commitment, we offer the following benefits:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive pay rates and weekly pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunities to work across various departments and sites, gaining invaluable knowledge and experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Priority of shifts over agency workers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An online self-booking system and dedicated bookings team, accommodating your convenience and availability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Electronic Timesheet submission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Onsite office and designated Business Partners to offer daily support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A professional AHP Recruitment Team that will ensure you are registered and compliant to work shifts as soon as possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated compliance team that will ensure you remain compliant to work, sending out regular expiry updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We also offer Core Skills Training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please apply directly to this advertisement by submitting you current CV, for further information on the roles please contact the Portsmouth Hospital Staff Bank Team on 0333 577 3316.&lt;/p&gt;
